      "tier": 2,
      "description": "Make a Move. During this movement you do not provoke Break Attacks and you may move through opponents with no penalty. You may not increase this movement with SP. Then, cast a Spell 6 against each figure moved through, ignoring SOI and Line of Sight. Roll your Casting die, Deal Magic DMG equal to the result and Inflict Darkness."
    },
    {
      "name": "In Dreams",
